        },
        {
            "title": "美國達拉斯移民和海關執法局發生槍擊事件 致多人受傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國國土安全部長克里斯蒂·諾姆表示，達拉斯移民和海關執法局(ICE)發生槍擊事件，造成「多人傷亡」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「槍手開槍自儘，」她周三在X上表示，並稱當局尚未確定其作案動機。據當地媒體報導，3人受傷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Shooting at Dallas ICE Center Leaves Multiple People Injured</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%94%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%92%8C%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E5%B1%80%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E8%87%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-131046161.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 22:20:48",
